312
00:20:17,863 --> 00:20:22,408
proud of this super colorful, super gay thing that we made that people seem to really like.

313
00:20:22,568 --> 00:20:26,872
This is some cool fan art that someone made. It's really cool. I'm very excited about this

314
00:20:27,793 --> 00:20:29,435
and I'm really proud of my team and

315
00:20:29,835 --> 00:20:34,819
I'm really proud of myself too for overcoming this really rough creative block and to be

