00:20:34,859 --> 00:20:39,843
able to have a list of tools that I can share with you and other people who might be experiencing

317
00:20:39,903 --> 00:20:45,067
creative block or who might know someone who is or may experience creative block in the

318
00:20:45,107 --> 00:20:45,407
future.

319
00:20:46,407 --> 00:20:51,515
So, in closing, if you're experiencing creative block, you are not a bad artist.

320
00:20:52,196 --> 00:20:55,140
If you're experiencing creative block, you are not a bad game designer.

